caption.text:
Over the past 15 months, I managed to get over 30 reels to go viral (1M+ views and more), along with many semi-viral ones (100K+ views).

Here’s what I found works best when creating viral content ideas:

Go to “Reels” and click on “Audio” (with or without an arrow).
Check the top 3 trending videos and read the comments (the comments should be from less than 7 days ago).
Use the audio in the same week you discover it.
Create smart, engaging text/hooks for your video.
HOOK STRATEGY: Your hook must be captivating, intriguing, aesthetic, relatable, or humorous! Grab the viewer’s attention within the first second, or they’ll scroll away. 📉

VALUE: Educate, inspire, motivate, provide fun ideas, or help the viewer in some way. 🙌🏼

Comment “Class,” and I’ll send you a totally free 4-lesson course on how to rapidly grow your brand on IG.

It will also show you how to monetize your audience with digital products.

See you there! 👋

caption.text:
Being a content creator is easy…

Said the person who’s never done it.

I’ve been a full-time content creator for 2 years and developed a system to turn content creation into a full-time career without relying on brand deals or burning out.

If you want to learn exactly how I did it, just comment “INFO” for more details. 🙏

…

Engaging captions: Make them short & valuable. 🧠

Most of your Instagram growth will come from a few viral reels. That’s how my personal brand skyrocketed—through a handful of viral hits.

caption.text:
Let’s be honest—humans can’t just do nothing.

Progress equals happiness, and while we might fantasize about not working, we’d soon get bored and unfulfilled.

That’s why creative work brings us the most joy.

Creating content and building your personal brand is one of the best ways to achieve this.

If you want to learn how I grew my personal brand to 500K+ followers and turned it into $500K in income, comment “Class” and I’ll send you a full course to get started.

caption.text:
It’s simpler than you think.

As a creative, you might overcomplicate things, but all you need is an audience and one product to hit $100K per year.

This is exactly what I teach in the Creator World.

If you’re ready to join our community and get support in building your dream content business, comment or DM me “Info” to get started.
